# Blok Design System

The marketplace app uses [Blok](https://blok.sitecore.com/) – Sitecore's design system built on shadcn/ui.

## Guidelines

1. **Use only Blok/shadcn components** for UI – no raw Radix primitives or custom UI libraries.
2. **Add components from Blok registry** when needed:
   ```bash
   npx shadcn@latest add https://blok.sitecore.com/r/theme.json
   npx shadcn@latest add https://blok.sitecore.com/r/dialog.json
   ```
3. **Theme first**: Add `theme.json` before other Blok components for design tokens.
4. **Import from `@/components/ui`** – components live in `packages/marketplace/src/components/ui/`.

See `packages/marketplace/BLOK.md` for full setup and component list.
